video.title: Ultimate Beastmaster Mexico
video.synopsis: Competitors representing countries from around the world battle it out on a grueling obstacle course. Luis Ernesto Franco and In√©s Sainz host.

episodes.synopsis: The first 12 competitors stare down the Beast. The one who racks up the most points will earn $10,000 and a spot in the final round.
episodes.title: Beast Nation

episodes.synopsis: An Olympic gold medalist dives into the competition, while another contestant literally loses his hair in the blood of the Beast.
episodes.title: Going for Gold

episodes.synopsis: The latest set of contestants tackle an all-new obstacle in Level 1, and those nimble enough to advance to Level 2 face an amped-up Spinal Descent.
episodes.title: The Beast Evolves

episodes.synopsis: A new twist makes Faceplant even more daunting. One competitor becomes the first ever to finish Level 2. A "Sasuke" champion takes on the Beast.
episodes.title: The Legend Vs. The Beast

episodes.synopsis: One contestant dominates the course through Level 3, but Level 4 still stands in the way of the $10,000 prize.
episodes.title: The Battle of Wills

episodes.synopsis: An 18-year-old student thinks she has what it takes to go farther than any woman so far. The upgraded Faceplant claims more victims.
episodes.title: Beauty Meets the Beast

episodes.synopsis: A competitor raises the bar with a record-setting performance, while another soldiers on through arm and leg injuries.
episodes.title: Beast Mode

episodes.synopsis: A pair of Korean brothers go head-to-head in the belly of the Beast. A crucial mistake could cost one finalist a chance at $10,000.
episodes.title: Brother Vs. Brother

episodes.synopsis: In the last qualifying round, the Digestive Track sends competitors plunging into the blood, while another contestant powers through bonus obstacles.
episodes.title: The Last Call

episodes.synopsis: In the championship round, tougher obstacles and new point thrusters test the nine winners as they pursue the "Ultimate Beastmaster" title.
episodes.title: Season One Finale

episodes.synopsis: For the first time, athletes from China, France, India, Italy and Spain join Americans to face off with the Beast for a $10,000 prize.
episodes.title: The Beast Within

episodes.synopsis: One contestant fights through a hard impact -- and a few stitches -- to get through Level 1. Competitors include a youth leader and a pole dancer.
episodes.title: Out For Blood

episodes.synopsis: The Beast swallows up a new crop of athletes that includes an ER doctor, a dance instructor, a pro freerunner and a body shop mechanic.
episodes.title: Taming The Beast

episodes.synopsis: New obstacles in Level 1 test a crop of Beastmaster hopefuls that includes mountaineers, physical therapists, a wrestling coach and an architect.
episodes.title: The Heart Of The Beast

episodes.synopsis: Competitors include a tattoo artist from Italy, a noodle bar owner from China, an Indian boxer and an American cheer coach.
episodes.title: The Beast Gets Schooled

episodes.synopsis: A wrestler, a pole vaulter, a diner owner and an MMA fighter are among those taking on the Beast. A creative strategic move shakes up Level 4.
episodes.title: The Battle Rages On

episodes.synopsis: The Beast takes aim at a couple as a husband and wife from China compete alongside a swimmer, a fashion designer and a church group leader.
episodes.title: Scaling The Beast

episodes.synopsis: A berth in Level 4 comes down to the wire on Hangman. Athletes include a break dancer, a speed skater, a stunt man and an Air Force medic.
episodes.title: Trapping The Beast

episodes.synopsis: Twin brothers from France hope to conquer the Beast, along with a boxer, an engineering student, a bikini fitness model and a motivational speaker.
episodes.title: Making The Cut

episodes.synopsis: The nine winners reconvene for one last run through the Beast with the grand prize of $50,000 and the title of Ultimate Beastmaster on the line.
episodes.title: A Beastmaster Is Crowned

episodes.synopsis: Nine new competitors face a Beast that's fiercer than ever. But only two will move on to the first semifinal round in "Beastmaster" history.
episodes.title: The Beast Evolves

episodes.synopsis: Two champion climbers are joined by a prizefighter, a powerlifter, a dance instructor, a surfer and others in a battle for two spots in the semifinals.
episodes.title: Champions Collide

episodes.synopsis: A new obstacle called "Rope Burn" challenges the third set of athletes. Two contestants become the last pair to qualify for the first semifinal.
episodes.title: Strive for Greatness

episodes.synopsis: Six qualifiers compete for three spots in the championship final, with a new twist that raises the intensity. One athlete hopes a big gamble pays off.
episodes.title: Semifinal #1

episodes.synopsis: The Beast evolves again with a new obstacle called "Rib Cage Row," and two of nine contenders will grab the first spots in the second semifinal.
episodes.title: A New Battle Begins

episodes.synopsis: The "Crash Pads" return, and a twisty new obstacle greets a group that includes the competition's youngest athlete and a cancer survivor.
episodes.title: Overcoming the Odds

episodes.synopsis: A group that includes a war hero and a survivor of Rwandan genocide confronts the hungry Beast with the last two semifinal berths at stake.
episodes.title: For the Glory

episodes.synopsis: With three spots left in the championship final, the second set of semifinalists faces the brutal task of racing through the entire Beast in one run.
episodes.title: Semifinal #2

episodes.synopsis: Of the 54 who dared to stare down the Beast, six remain. Only one will best the competition to claim $50,000 and the "Ultimate Beastmaster" crown.
episodes.title: The Ultimate Beastmaster Championship
